    "id": 5,
    "title": "FizzBuzz Single",
    "difficulty": "Medium",
    "description": "Read an integer N. Print \"FizzBuzz\" if N is divisible by both 3 and 5, \"Fizz\" if divisible by only 3, \"Buzz\" if divisible by only 5, or the number itself otherwise.",
